{"tid":1632661,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"致勇武：喺生死關頭靠晒你地，求你地平時交畀和理非可以嘛？","createTime":"2019-10-06T19:30:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T06:34:55.000Z","uid":315038,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f8cc6169ac680bac22feff7081b373f7374e37f3","tid":1632661,"uid":315038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:30:33.000Z","msg":"記唔記得你地<span style=\"color: red;\">最自豪</span>嘅係邊件事？<br />\n係6.12<br />\n個個成日loop「如果唔係班後生仔衝嘅話，送中喺6.12過咗架喇！」<br />\n6.12係<span style=\"color: red;\">生死關頭</span>，<span style=\"color: red;\">呢啲生死關頭全世界靠晒你地</span><br />\n<br />\n記唔記得你地<span style=\"color: red;\">最令人感動</span>嘅係邊件事？<br />\n係6.16 + 8.18<br />\n當時民間不斷強調要絕對和平咁遊行/集會<br />\n結果你地非常配合，喺8.18仲有<span style=\"color: red;\">和勇互抱</span>嘅感人場面<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">全世界都注視</span><br />\n<br />\n大家都明白<span style=\"color: red;\">勇武好無私</span>，為咗保護手足甘願企到最前<span style=\"color: red;\">擋子彈</span><br />\n中排嘅滅煙隊每次出勤都令到和理非受少好多苦<br />\n撤退嘅時候又幫我地拖住班狗，確保我地安全離開<br />\n當黑社會同暴徒藍絲襲擊我地，勇武又會還拖保護我地<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">勇武喺今場運動之中係好偉大</span></span><br />\n<br />\n但係，勇武知道而家<span style=\"color: red;\">我地欠咩嘢先可以嬴</span>嘛？<br />\n係<span style=\"color: red;\">和理非嘅痛苦</span>，甚至<span style=\"color: red;\">犧牲</span><br />\n而家要推林鄭政權落台，係要靠摧毀佢嘅<span style=\"color: red;\">道德基礎</span><br />\n民意點解一直與大家同在？<br />\n外國點解不斷聲援大家？<br />\n係因為林鄭政權<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不道德</span></span><br />\n要進一步摧毀林鄭嘅道德基礎，就要<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">靠和理非嘅痛苦+犧牲</span></span><br />\n<br />\n點解林鄭同黑警要滲透我地，要嫁禍我地，要挑動你地出手，要挑動你地破壞？<br />\n係<span style=\"color: red;\">因為佢要打擊<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地嘅道德基礎</span></span><br />\n<br />\n所以，求求你地：<br />\n只做<span style=\"color: red;\">滅煙工作</span><br />\n只喺<span style=\"color: red;\">生死關頭出手</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好</span>再為和理非擋子彈<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好</span>再保護和理非<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好</span>再喺撤退嘅時候為和理非拖延<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好</span>再為和理非還拖</span>(你地受攻擊自衞除外)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">真係唔使保護和理非</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">畀和理非受傷甚至犧牲</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地出得嚟預咗架喇</span></span><br />\n<br />\n最後，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">花廿分鐘睇咗呢條片佢</span>，由4:48開始睇<br />\n佢代表我嘅立場，亦代表好多膠撚嘅立場：<br />\n(好遺憾，和理非大部份都係膠撚)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YYBWZ5HvJw4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DYYBWZ5HvJw4&d=QZYHYFPECKJw76TN47EEprM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=712942ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YYBWZ5HvJw4</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">回頭是岸 勿忘初衷<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span><br />\n<br />\nP牌推唔郁，求幫推"},{"pid":"907e494c7aae5953dc7bfa661fe58c1866dbb5d9","tid":1632661,"uid":284304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:31:06.000Z","msg":"[文長]分析Solomon教你打美國戰線<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ejovdS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ejovdS</a>"},{"pid":"fae56073648c479aa98c6c3f1bb384b31ba52e88","tid":1632661,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:31:52.000Z","msg":"［分化收皮］香港01分化民陣失敗，聲稱裝修過火、民意逆轉<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1632454\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1632454</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"333d9f9f160bae65a8cd113d6a963b2b00d16b02","tid":1632661,"uid":315038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:32:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"11ddf1b57b214c8e2de69cda6aeb19a977ffeb48","tid":1632661,"uid":315038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:33:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"027f5fcb6d4bf61209b7f3d1d38172